    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered since day one. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014not a single scratch to be found! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
