    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage since day one, resulting in a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats still retain their original scent, and every electronic component functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a full, documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a pristine undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Serious inquiries only for this turn-key masterpiece.",
